# Gurmad Sanitation - Child Safety Standards

At Gurmad Sanitation, we are committed to maintaining a safe environment for all users and complying with Google's [Child Safety Standards](https://support.google.com/googleplay/android-developer/answer/10144311).

## Our Commitment

We do **not** allow any form of:
- Child Sexual Abuse Material (CSAM)
- Inappropriate content targeting minors
- Exploitation or endangerment of children

Our app does not include user-generated content or communication features that could expose users to unsafe behavior. Our platform is intended for adult use only (18+) for utility and sanitation services.

## Reporting Concerns

If you encounter any suspicious or harmful activity related to our platform, please report it immediately to:

**Email:** gurmadwaste2@gmail.com  
**Subject Line:** Child Safety Concern

## Contact for Compliance

The designated contact person responsible for child safety standards compliance is:

**Name:** Gurmad Sanitation Compliance Officer  
**Email:** gurmadwaste2@gmail.com 
**Phone:** +252 63 7478888

## Updates and Enforcement

We regularly review our policies and update them in line with best practices for child safety. Any violations are taken seriously and may result in removal from our platform and notification of authorities where required.

